T*
(has a new option to request it falls back to another model automatically if something gets) Tj
T*
(rejected. Claude Mythos 5 is out today as well, Anthropic say it "Shares Claude Fable 5's) Tj
T*
(capabilities without the safety classifiers". The models have a 1 million token context window,) Tj
T*
(128,000 maximum output tokens and a knowledge cut-off date of January 2026. They are priced at) Tj
T*
(twice the price of Claude Opus 4.5/4.6/4.7/4.8: $10/million input tokens and $50/m...) Tj
